{"code":0,"data":[{"cid":59165,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Alice","permissions":["report"],"pid":10084,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"隔壁p也不是pku","timestamp":1593347699,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":59192,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Bob","permissions":["report"],"pid":10084,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Alice: p当然是pku","timestamp":1593347992,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":59342,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Alice","permissions":["report"],"pid":10084,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Bob: 咱们的p是pku，隔壁的p是powerful","timestamp":1593349609,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":59434,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Bob","permissions":["report"],"pid":10084,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Alice: 咦 还真是\n见到#3617了","timestamp":1593351040,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":431463,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Carol","permissions":["report"],"pid":10084,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"北京时间5月12日，NBA正式官宣，马晓飞（Michael Ma）将出任NBA中国新一任CEO，这也是迄今为止第一位中国大陆出身的NBA中国掌门人。\n\n值得一提的是，马晓飞的父亲是中国体育产业泰斗、央视体育频道创始人马国力。\n\n显然，在NBA在中国陷入历史最困难阶段的当下，NBA尤其渴望选择一位熟悉中国国情、能够引领NBA中国破冰的新掌门，而马晓飞的履历、资源、人脉在这方面具有独特优势。并且，这些独特优势决定了NBA总部信任他、NBA中国团队信服他、中国方面认可他，这三点决定了他就是现阶段最合适的人选。\n\n在这种大背景下，尽管马晓飞人脉丰富、颇受中国方面认可，又与央视上下颇为熟悉，但面对NBA此前铸下的原则性错误，恐怕他也很难在短期内让双方关系立时缓和。所以，即便再乐观的人也不应该指望NBA在中国的破冰过程可以一蹴而就。","timestamp":1602273241,"type":"text","url":""}],"post":{"attention":false,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"likenum":2,"permissions":["report","fold"],"pid":10084,"reply":5,"tag":null,"text":"#412t不是thu差评","timestamp":1593347412,"type":"text","updated_at":1606782587,"url":"","vote":{}}}